{"tid":2051334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"德國手足高舉“Free Hong Kong”標語!入去多謝人!","createTime":"2020-06-04T16:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T05:03:26.000Z","uid":25951,"like":83,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f79a5f7eddd0b34158602c22b6b752602ada137d","tid":2051334,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110976485656573/posts/2955543857866474?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110976485656573%2Fposts%2F2955543857866474%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=98093e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110976485656573/posts/2955543857866474?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n朋友翻譯:<br />\n&ldquo;1989年6月4日有好多學生喺北京天安門為民主示威, 呢個示威最後被軍事鎮壓, 有約一千個年輕人死咗。<br />\n今日喺香港同樣有好多人爭取梗民主同自由, 同樣對抗梗中國政府既極權。我地嘅訴求好清晰, 就係唔想有第二次嘅天安門事件, 因此我地今日站喺香港民主嘅一方, 並喺中國大使館門外為一個自由既香港示威。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n每次見到有鬼佬支持香港都覺得好滾動, 大家入去個post度多謝德國手足喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NGOGcH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NGOGcH.png&h=43e8041f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eca5e3d49db0ec849523debfa198337dce26f5e5","tid":2051334,"uid":25951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:50:51.000Z","msg":"Stand with Hong Kong"},{"pid":"025da8556ddc07b129eb8159c768e1373d09e760","tid":2051334,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國際線，free HK!"},{"pid":"8044ad3ee76d300944d97e4f8b0a4a69a87447eb","tid":2051334,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"Fight for freedom"},{"pid":"c4e071ecb1ca51f150894f1b1afa07656b07a5d7","tid":2051334,"uid":2